text.tspan: Bring this boarding pass with you as dead tree to receive an expedited registration at the conference. Please check
the details on this boarding pass before coming to the conference. Report errors to contact@lca2013.linux.org.au
Registration will be at John XXIII between 2pm and 6pm on Sunday 27 January. Keynotes are at Llewllyn Hall. Registration at other
times is at the Manning Clarke Center, which is the main conference venue. If you need urgent assistance, please call our oncall
phone on 0429 929 812. For non-urgent assistance, please email contact@lca2013.linux.org.au.
